{
  "stem": "3380.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't like what either one of us were doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we always used to have-- we always used to have the Jewish paper, the Polish paper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the elderly people-- the people, I mean, they-- for them, the-- the-- the news was the They were also interested in what goes on in the world.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't get me wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not fanatic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the most important thing for them then, that was the And--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing but Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We talked Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since Hitler came to power, in 1933, they came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism was, in Poland, very, very strong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't like the Jews, either-- even before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was somehow-- that was-- Pilsudski had the power.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he was the prime minister in Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, that was not-- that didn't came out until, really, Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they have seen what Hitler is trying to do with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to an extent, that-- that-- they were happy to see it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were very unfriendly to the Jewish people-- the Polish-- the Polacks, I mean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I mean, you had signs that shouldn't-- nobody should buy by Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Prior.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, yeah, that was-- after Hitler, that was all over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wherever you went, I mean, you could see signs on every street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, you know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on --on the houses, on the-- wherever you went, I mean, you could see and [SPEAKING POLISH] I mean, that's mean that you shouldn't buy by-- by Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH] Don't buy by a Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do not buy by Jew-- over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I mean, that was-- that-- that-- that-- for a slogan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, that the-- they should go to their own stores.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
